<p>Is there build-in mechanism in angular to create collection views? I have a collaction of data which are mapped to form like that:</p>  <pre><code>&lt;from&gt;     &lt;input type="checkbox"/&gt; {{value1}} &lt;br/&gt;     &lt;input type="checkbox"/&gt; {{value2}} &lt;br/&gt;     &lt;input type="button" value="prev"/&gt;     &lt;input type="button" value="next"/&gt; &lt;/from&gt; </code></pre>  <p>E.g. a collection is fetched, then form is displayed for first value, user click on check boxes and go to next form with next value and etc. Is there build-in mechanism in angular for such situations?</p>